{"tid":1450790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"#108337 泡沫花火 分化狗專叫人塞鐵","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:56:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:10:53.000Z","uid":196227,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"edfa43e55af7a80be790c052f5f2a36dc963955a","tid":1450790,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:56:57.000Z","msg":"突然聽日要塞鐵件事好鬼<br />\n<br />\n任何不合作運動都係要一定時間文宣<br />\n班分化狗好似想轉移今日焦點<br />\n唔比時間我們做大文宣<br />\n等聽日普通市民淨係知有人塞鐵<br />\n理性分析都知做現時最好行動<br />\n<br />\n聽日要臨時和理非入機場我好支持<br />\n塞鐵你就收皮啦<br />\n<br />\n#108337 泡沫花火<br />\n任何理性解釋唔好塞鐵都會入去屌人<br />\n叫佢講論點淨係識負皮<br />\n冇開任何post<br />\n完全唔知咩立場<br />\n仲鬼過p牌仔<br />\n<br />\n各位小心呢條友<br />\n屌你分化狗<br />\n見到就夠膽入黎屌柒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be859ef59a707fc312089bd57be439787c80fb82","tid":1450790,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:59:43.000Z","msg":"[url]唔好塞鐵，有預告嘅屌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1450071</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n詳情理由入去呢個post睇<br />\n<br />\n總結小小<br />\n-大媽group一早有消息<br />\n-有公司都通知定員工<br />\n-聽日塞鐵只會轉移今日焦點"},{"pid":"5c7ddb4ffc266d51d0a3df9e1eef39023a56c2a0","tid":1450790,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"推到呢條仆街入黎澄清<br />\n或者繼續負評我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad0ca9171c2b1f00fa2e918b0c43da5d6d32520e","tid":1450790,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:03:28.000Z","msg":"澄清呀撚樣"},{"pid":"48c7b7fadbbc7fd7da50115c8488da52548ba539","tid":1450790,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"推 上星期先講完唔好塞住 要搞就搞機場"},{"pid":"7a2949e0d89020bc01d891bdb4e8f7df22ac1273","tid":1450790,"uid":196227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48c7b7fadbbc7fd7da50115c8488da52548ba539","tid":1450